track.name: Syeeda's Song Flute
comments: My foot is out of control :-)
Makes me crave a great cup of coffee for some reason...
The tune has some similarity to "Nardis".

continuous and beautiful as a stream of consciousness and the air stream can be without effort or so it seems a calm flow of tenor, drums, bass and piano..............seamless and sensitive, searching and sure, simple and smooth.
Amazing... Is it from his drugs period?
wow... Who's on that piano? Blakey maybe???
Superb playing from everybody. I love it.
